          "instruction": "Answer the questions based on the audio.",
          "prompt_html": "<h1>MULTIPLE CHOICE 59</h1><p><strong>Questions 11 - 14</strong></p><p>Choose the correct letter <strong>A, B or C</strong>.</p><p>11 What is the main difference between these kayaks and a canoe?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong></th><th>Your legs are not enclosed in the kayak.</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong></td><td>They are made from different materials.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong></td><td>The two boats are very different shapes.</td></tr></tbody></table><p>12 What do some beginners not like about the kayak?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong></th><th>Getting into the water takes longer.</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong></td><td>They feel less secure.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong></td><td>The seating position is not as comfortable.</td></tr></tbody></table><p>13 What should you do if you fall in the water?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong></th><th>Get back onto the boat as quickly as possible.</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong></td><td>Wait in the water.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong></td><td>Swim to the shore.</td></tr></tbody></table><p>14 What is the problem with some of the clothes people are wearing?</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong></th><th>They are not wearing the correct safety equipment.</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong></td><td>The clothes are not warm enough.</td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong></td><td>The clothes are difficult to swim in.</td></tr></tbody></table>",
